consistent brand style.

00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:08.890
And I'm particularly impressed
by their icon, which is both a

00:11:08.890 --> 00:11:11.930
distinctive silhouette and also
offers a really excellent

00:11:11.930 --> 00:11:14.932
indication of what
the app offers.

