There's sort of four key
things that you need to

00:19:00.240 --> 00:19:02.230
consider to even be
in the running for

00:19:02.230 --> 00:19:03.750
us to consider you.

00:19:03.750 --> 00:19:07.650
And those are great assets,
having a great quality app,

00:19:07.650 --> 00:19:09.980
having a great quality tablet
app, and following the Android

00:19:09.980 --> 00:19:10.840
design guidelines.

00:19:10.840 --> 00:19:13.555
Let's look at each of these in
a little bit more detail.

00:19:13.555 --> 00:19:15.180
IAN NI-LEWIS: These really
are pretty basic.

00:19:15.180 --> 00:19:19.260
I mean, for the assets, we're
looking for something that's

00:19:19.260 --> 00:19:22.590
going to help us help you
sell your application.

00:19:22.590 --> 00:19:25.790
The people that work for Google
Play really want to

00:19:25.790 --> 00:19:26.880
help you sell your app.

00:19:26.880 --> 00:19:30.620
But they can't do that if your
assets look like garbage.

00:19:30.620 --> 00:19:32.590
RETO MEIER: Or if they're
