00:19:32.590 --> 00:19:32.880
All right?

00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:35.800
So we can't-- we will probably
not even look at your app on

00:19:35.800 --> 00:19:38.600
the clinic if you don't at
least have your feature

00:19:38.600 --> 00:19:41.710
graphic, basically all of the
assets which you need to

00:19:41.710 --> 00:19:43.130
specify in Google Play done.

